trans-unit.source: The MsmqIntegrationSecurity class encapsulates the transport security settings for the Message Queuing (MSMQ) integration channel.
trans-unit.target: A classe MsmqIntegrationSecurity encapsula as configurações de segurança de transporte para o canal de integração de enfileiramento de mensagens (MSMQ).

trans-unit.source: The Message Queuing integration channel enables [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] applications to communicate with existing Message Queuing applications.
trans-unit.target: O canal de integração de enfileiramento de mensagens permite que [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] aplicativos se comuniquem com aplicativos de enfileiramento de mensagens existentes.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode"></xref> that is associated with the Message Queuing (MSMQ) integration channel.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode"> </xref> que está associado com o canal de integração de enfileiramento de mensagens (MSMQ).

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode> is an enumeration that contains the following values: <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode>é uma enumeração que contém os seguintes valores: <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode>e <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode> </xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode></xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode"></xref> that is associated with the Message Queuing integration channel.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqIntegrationSecurityMode"> </xref> que está associado com o canal de integração de enfileiramento de mensagens.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"></xref> that is associated with the Message Queuing (MSMQ) integration channel.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"> </xref> que está associado com o canal de integração de enfileiramento de mensagens (MSMQ).

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity> encapsulates the security settings for the Message Queuing integration transport.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity>encapsula as configurações de segurança para o transporte de integração de enfileiramento de mensagens.</xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity>

trans-unit.source: The settings are the same for both the Message Queuing integration and queued transports.
trans-unit.target: As configurações são as mesmas para a integração de enfileiramento de mensagens e de transportes na fila.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity> enables you to set the Authentication Mode, Encryption Algorithm, Secure Hash Algorithm, and Protection Level.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity>permite que você defina o modo de autenticação, o algoritmo de criptografia, algoritmo de Hash seguro e nível de proteção.</xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"></xref> that is associated with the Message Queuing integration channel.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"> </xref> que está associado com o canal de integração de enfileiramento de mensagens.
